{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":1212,"text":"I'm not sure that every person here"},{"time":3342,"text":"is familiar with my pictures."},{"time":6079,"text":"I want to start to show just a few pictures to you,"},{"time":10162,"text":"and after I'll speak."}]},{"cues":[{"time":45884,"text":"I must speak to you a little bit of my history,"},{"time":49836,"text":"because we'll be speaking on this"},{"time":51783,"text":"during my speech here."},{"time":54764,"text":"I was born in 1944 in Brazil,"},{"time":57900,"text":"in the times that Brazil was not yet a market economy."},{"time":61655,"text":"I was born on a farm,"},{"time":63538,"text":"a farm that was more than 50 percent rainforest [still]."},{"time":68040,"text":"A marvelous place."},{"time":69660,"text":"I lived with incredible birds, incredible animals,"},{"time":73972,"text":"I swam in our small rivers with our caimans."},{"time":78213,"text":"It was about 35 families that lived on this farm,"},{"time":81122,"text":"and everything that we produced on this farm, we consumed."},{"time":85404,"text":"Very few things went to the market."},{"time":87511,"text":"Once a year, the only thing that went to the market"},{"time":90221,"text":"was the cattle that we produced,"},{"time":91941,"text":"and we made trips of about 45 days"},{"time":94710,"text":"to reach the slaughterhouse,"},{"time":96886,"text":"bringing thousands of head of cattle,"},{"time":99180,"text":"and about 20 days traveling back"},{"time":101712,"text":"to reach our farm again."}]},{"cues":[{"time":104109,"text":"When I was 15 years old,"},{"time":106486,"text":"it was necessary for me to leave this place"},{"time":109991,"text":"and go to a town a little bit bigger -- much bigger --"},{"time":113454,"text":"where I did the second part of secondary school."},{"time":116885,"text":"There I learned different things."},{"time":119653,"text":"Brazil was starting to urbanize, industrialize,"},{"time":122278,"text":"and I knew the politics. I became a little bit radical,"},{"time":126693,"text":"I was a member of leftist parties,"},{"time":129535,"text":"and I became an activist."},{"time":132641,"text":"I [went to] university to become an economist."},{"time":135733,"text":"I [did] a master's degree in economics."}]},{"cues":[{"time":138413,"text":"And the most important thing in my life"},{"time":141422,"text":"also happened in this time."},{"time":143081,"text":"I met an incredible girl"},{"time":145770,"text":"who became my lifelong best friend,"},{"time":149908,"text":"and my associate in everything that I have done till now,"},{"time":153676,"text":"my wife, Lélia Wanick Salgado."}]},{"cues":[{"time":156940,"text":"Brazil radicalized very strongly."},{"time":158844,"text":"We fought very hard against the dictatorship,"},{"time":161756,"text":"in a moment it was necessary to us:"},{"time":163542,"text":"Either go into clandestinity with weapons in hand,"},{"time":167126,"text":"or leave Brazil. We were too young,"},{"time":169581,"text":"and our organization thought it was better for us to go out,"},{"time":174782,"text":"and we went to France,"},{"time":175746,"text":"where I did a PhD in economics,"},{"time":177765,"text":"Léila became an architect."},{"time":179761,"text":"I worked after for an investment bank."},{"time":182844,"text":"We made a lot of trips, financed development,"},{"time":185806,"text":"economic projects in Africa with the World Bank."}]},{"cues":[{"time":188661,"text":"And one day photography made a total invasion in my life."},{"time":192129,"text":"I became a photographer,"},{"time":193367,"text":"abandoned everything and became a photographer,"},{"time":195983,"text":"and I started to do the photography"},{"time":198808,"text":"that was important for me."},{"time":201804,"text":"Many people tell me that you are a photojournalist,"},{"time":203990,"text":"that you are an anthropologist photographer,"},{"time":206566,"text":"that you are an activist photographer."},{"time":209327,"text":"But I did much more than that."},{"time":212327,"text":"I put photography as my life."},{"time":215009,"text":"I lived totally inside photography"},{"time":217613,"text":"doing long term projects,"},{"time":219648,"text":"and I want to show you just a few pictures"},{"time":222158,"text":"of -- again, you'll see inside the social projects,"},{"time":228055,"text":"that I went to, I published many books"},{"time":230217,"text":"on these photographs,"},{"time":233423,"text":"but I'll just show you a few ones now."}]},{"cues":[{"time":282949,"text":"In the '90s, from 1994 to 2000,"},{"time":286724,"text":"I photographed a story called Migrations."},{"time":289965,"text":"It became a book. It became a show."}]},{"cues":[{"time":291842,"text":"But during the time that I was photographing this,"},{"time":294600,"text":"I lived through a very hard moment in my life, mostly in Rwanda."},{"time":300337,"text":"I saw in Rwanda total brutality."},{"time":304648,"text":"I saw deaths by thousands per day."},{"time":307813,"text":"I lost my faith in our species."},{"time":310754,"text":"I didn't believe that it was possible for us to live any longer,"},{"time":314945,"text":"and I started to be attacked by my own Staphylococcus."},{"time":320492,"text":"I started to have infection everywhere."},{"time":323476,"text":"When I made love with my wife, I had no sperm that came out of me;"},{"time":327888,"text":"I had blood."},{"time":330715,"text":"I went to see a friend's doctor in Paris,"},{"time":333596,"text":"told him that I was completely sick."},{"time":336362,"text":"He made a long examination, and told me, \"Sebastian,"},{"time":339216,"text":"you are not sick, your prostate is perfect."},{"time":342353,"text":"What happened is, you saw so many deaths that you are dying."},{"time":346441,"text":"You must stop. Stop."},{"time":349360,"text":"You must stop because on the contrary, you will be dead.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":354201,"text":"And I made the decision to stop."},{"time":357847,"text":"I was really upset with photography,"},{"time":360140,"text":"with everything in the world,"},{"time":362161,"text":"and I made the decision to go back to where I was born."},{"time":366001,"text":"It was a big coincidence."},{"time":367605,"text":"It was the moment that my parents became very old."},{"time":371016,"text":"I have seven sisters. I'm one of the only men in my family,"},{"time":374577,"text":"and they made together the decision"},{"time":376445,"text":"to transfer this land to Léila and myself."},{"time":379145,"text":"When we received this land, this land was as dead as I was."},{"time":384761,"text":"When I was a kid, it was more than 50 percent rainforest."},{"time":388065,"text":"When we received the land,"},{"time":389587,"text":"it was less than half a percent rainforest,"},{"time":393362,"text":"as in all my region."},{"time":395007,"text":"To build development, Brazilian development,"},{"time":397936,"text":"we destroyed a lot of our forest."},{"time":400723,"text":"As you did here in the United States,"},{"time":402706,"text":"or you did in India, everywhere in this planet."},{"time":404994,"text":"To build our development,"},{"time":406672,"text":"we come to a huge contradiction"},{"time":408755,"text":"that we destroy around us everything."},{"time":412490,"text":"This farm that had thousands of head of cattle"},{"time":416155,"text":"had just a few hundreds,"},{"time":418322,"text":"and we didn't know how to deal with these."},{"time":420727,"text":"And Léila came up with an incredible idea, a crazy idea."}]},{"cues":[{"time":424627,"text":"She said, why don't you put back the rainforest that was here before?"},{"time":429274,"text":"You say that you were born in paradise."},{"time":430780,"text":"Let's build the paradise again."}]},{"cues":[{"time":433706,"text":"And I went to see a good friend"},{"time":436538,"text":"that was engineering forests"},{"time":438071,"text":"to prepare a project for us,"},{"time":439969,"text":"and we started. We started to plant, and this"},{"time":442150,"text":"first year we lost a lot of trees, second year less,"},{"time":446407,"text":"and slowly, slowly this dead land started to be born again."},{"time":451468,"text":"We started to plant hundreds of thousands of trees,"},{"time":454831,"text":"only local species, only native species,"},{"time":458271,"text":"where we built an ecosystem identical to the one that was destroyed,"},{"time":461812,"text":"and the life started to come back in an incredible way."},{"time":466120,"text":"It was necessary for us to transform our land"},{"time":468919,"text":"into a national park."},{"time":470361,"text":"We transformed. We gave this land back to nature."},{"time":473019,"text":"It became a national park."},{"time":474394,"text":"We created an institution called Instituto Terra,"},{"time":478144,"text":"and we built a big environmental project to raise money everywhere."},{"time":483123,"text":"Here in Los Angeles, in the Bay Area in San Francisco,"},{"time":486908,"text":"it became tax deductible in the United States."},{"time":489059,"text":"We raised money in Spain, in Italy, a lot in Brazil."},{"time":492387,"text":"We worked with a lot of companies in Brazil"},{"time":494595,"text":"that put money into this project, the government."},{"time":496843,"text":"And the life started to come, and I had a big wish"},{"time":501027,"text":"to come back to photography, to photograph again."},{"time":504443,"text":"And this time, my wish was not to photograph anymore"},{"time":507738,"text":"just one animal that I had photographed all my life: us."},{"time":512321,"text":"I wished to photograph the other animals,"},{"time":514689,"text":"to photograph the landscapes,"},{"time":516681,"text":"to photograph us, but us from the beginning,"},{"time":520127,"text":"the time we lived in equilibrium with nature."},{"time":522657,"text":"And I went. I started in the beginning of 2004,"},{"time":527210,"text":"and I finished at the end of 2011."},{"time":530410,"text":"We created an incredible amount of pictures,"},{"time":533103,"text":"and the result -- Lélia did the design of all my books,"},{"time":536673,"text":"the design of all my shows. She is the creator of the shows."},{"time":539737,"text":"And what we want with these pictures"},{"time":542044,"text":"is to create a discussion about what we have that is pristine on the planet"},{"time":548456,"text":"and what we must hold on this planet"},{"time":550979,"text":"if we want to live, to have some equilibrium in our life."},{"time":554277,"text":"And I wanted to see us"},{"time":556788,"text":"when we used, yes, our instruments in stone."},{"time":562655,"text":"We exist yet. I was last week"},{"time":564812,"text":"at the Brazilian National Indian Foundation,"},{"time":567708,"text":"and only in the Amazon we have about 110 groups"},{"time":571014,"text":"of Indians that are not contacted yet."},{"time":573945,"text":"We must protect the forest in this sense."},{"time":576478,"text":"And with these pictures, I hope that we can create"},{"time":581313,"text":"information, a system of information."},{"time":583542,"text":"We tried to do a new presentation of the planet,"},{"time":587288,"text":"and I want to show you now just a few pictures"},{"time":589214,"text":"of this project, please."}]},{"cues":[{"time":707543,"text":"Well, this — (Applause) —"},{"time":709975,"text":"Thank you. Thank you very much."}]},{"cues":[{"time":717142,"text":"This is what we must fight hard"},{"time":720228,"text":"to hold like it is now."},{"time":722119,"text":"But there is another part that we must together rebuild,"},{"time":726230,"text":"to build our societies, our modern family of societies,"},{"time":730247,"text":"we are at a point where we cannot go back."},{"time":732886,"text":"But we create an incredible contradiction."},{"time":735094,"text":"To build all this, we destroy a lot."},{"time":737390,"text":"Our forest in Brazil, that antique forest"},{"time":739600,"text":"that was the size of California,"},{"time":742486,"text":"is destroyed today 93 percent."},{"time":745160,"text":"Here, on the West Coast, you've destroyed your forest."},{"time":748154,"text":"Around here, no? The redwood forests are gone."},{"time":751391,"text":"Gone very fast, disappeared."},{"time":753258,"text":"Coming the other day from Atlanta, here, two days ago,"},{"time":755927,"text":"I was flying over deserts"},{"time":757771,"text":"that we made, we provoked with our own hands."},{"time":760631,"text":"India has no more trees. Spain has no more trees."}]},{"cues":[{"time":763290,"text":"And we must rebuild these forests."},{"time":766799,"text":"That is the essence of our life, these forests."},{"time":770447,"text":"We need to breathe. The only factory"},{"time":774689,"text":"capable to transform CO2 into oxygen,"},{"time":778265,"text":"are the forests."},{"time":780009,"text":"The only machine capable to capture the carbon"},{"time":784363,"text":"that we are producing, always,"},{"time":787214,"text":"even if we reduce them, everything that we do, we produce CO2,"},{"time":791379,"text":"are the trees."},{"time":792878,"text":"I put the question -- three or four weeks ago,"},{"time":797244,"text":"we saw in the newspapers"},{"time":798933,"text":"millions of fish that die in Norway."},{"time":801825,"text":"A lack of oxygen in the water."},{"time":804841,"text":"I put to myself the question, if for a moment,"},{"time":807073,"text":"we will not lack oxygen for all animal species,"},{"time":811060,"text":"ours included -- that would be very complicated for us."}]},{"cues":[{"time":814498,"text":"For the water system, the trees are essential."},{"time":818802,"text":"I'll give you a small example that you'll understand very easily."},{"time":822474,"text":"You happy people that have a lot of hair on your head,"},{"time":826400,"text":"if you take a shower, it takes you"},{"time":829565,"text":"two or three hours to dry your hair"},{"time":833089,"text":"if you don't use a dryer machine."},{"time":835410,"text":"Me, one minute, it's dry. The same with the trees."},{"time":840191,"text":"The trees are the hair of our planet."},{"time":842893,"text":"When you have rain in a place that has no trees,"},{"time":846682,"text":"in just a few minutes, the water arrives in the stream,"},{"time":850110,"text":"brings soil, destroying our water source,"},{"time":852693,"text":"destroying the rivers,"},{"time":854600,"text":"and no humidity to retain."},{"time":856010,"text":"When you have trees, the root system holds the water."},{"time":860301,"text":"All the branches of the trees, the leaves that come down"},{"time":863029,"text":"create a humid area,"},{"time":865091,"text":"and they take months and months under the water, go to the rivers,"},{"time":869811,"text":"and maintain our source, maintain our rivers."},{"time":873011,"text":"This is the most important thing,"},{"time":875015,"text":"when we imagine that we need water for every activity in life."}]},{"cues":[{"time":879478,"text":"I want to show you now, to finish,"},{"time":881666,"text":"just a few pictures that for me"},{"time":884366,"text":"are very important in that direction."},{"time":887305,"text":"You remember that I told you,"},{"time":889455,"text":"when I received the farm from my parents"},{"time":891558,"text":"that was my paradise, that was the farm."},{"time":894358,"text":"Land completely destroyed, the erosion there, the land had dried."},{"time":899868,"text":"But you can see in this picture,"},{"time":902424,"text":"we were starting to construct an educational center"},{"time":906439,"text":"that became quite a large environmental center in Brazil."},{"time":911403,"text":"But you see a lot of small spots in this picture."},{"time":915741,"text":"In each point of those spots, we had planted a tree."},{"time":919318,"text":"There are thousands of trees."},{"time":920893,"text":"Now I'll show you the pictures made exactly in the same point"},{"time":924101,"text":"two months ago."}]},{"cues":[{"time":927807,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":936857,"text":"I told you in the beginning that it was necessary"},{"time":938615,"text":"for us to plant about 2.5 million trees"},{"time":943415,"text":"of about 200 different species"},{"time":945854,"text":"in order to rebuild the ecosystem."},{"time":949094,"text":"And I'll show you the last picture."},{"time":951629,"text":"We are with two million trees in the ground now."},{"time":954798,"text":"We are doing the sequestration"},{"time":956447,"text":"of about 100,000 tons of carbon with these trees."}]},{"cues":[{"time":960901,"text":"My friends, it's very easy to do. We did it, no?"},{"time":965445,"text":"By an accident that happened to me,"},{"time":967757,"text":"we went back, we built an ecosystem."},{"time":971157,"text":"We here inside the room,"},{"time":973824,"text":"I believe that we have the same concern,"},{"time":977360,"text":"and the model that we created in Brazil,"},{"time":979796,"text":"we can transplant it here."},{"time":981141,"text":"We can apply it everywhere around the world, no?"},{"time":984164,"text":"And I believe that we can do it together."}]},{"cues":[{"time":987112,"text":"Thank you very much."}]},{"cues":[{"time":988741,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}